# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Fastlane Fastfile - Android Automation Lanes
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#
# Usage:
#   cd android
#   fastlane build_debug        → Build debug APK
#   fastlane build_release      → Build release APK
#   fastlane distribute         → Build + Upload to Firebase
#   fastlane deploy_internal    → Deploy to Google Play (internal testing)
#
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

default_platform(:android)

platform :android do

  # ─────────────────────────────────────────────
  # 🧹 HELPER: Clean and get dependencies
  # ─────────────────────────────────────────────
  before_all do
    sh("cd ../.. && flutter clean")
    sh("cd ../.. && flutter pub get")
  end

  # ─────────────────────────────────────────────
  # 🔨 Lane: Build Debug APK
  # ─────────────────────────────────────────────
  desc "Build a debug APK"
  lane :build_debug do
    sh("cd ../.. && flutter build apk --debug")
    UI.success("✅ Debug APK built successfully!")
    UI.message("📦 APK Location: build/app/outputs/flutter-apk/app-debug.apk")
  end

  # ─────────────────────────────────────────────
  # 🔨 Lane: Build Release APK
  # ─────────────────────────────────────────────
  desc "Build a release APK"
  lane :build_release do
    sh("cd ../.. && flutter build apk --release")
    UI.success("✅ Release APK built successfully!")
    UI.message("📦 APK Location: build/app/outputs/flutter-apk/app-release.apk")
  end

  # ─────────────────────────────────────────────
  # 🔥 Lane: Build + Distribute to Firebase
  # ─────────────────────────────────────────────
  desc "Build release APK and distribute to Firebase App Distribution"
  lane :distribute do
    # Step 1: Build
    build_release

    # Step 2: Upload to Firebase App Distribution
    firebase_app_distribution(
      app: ENV["FIREBASE_APP_ID"] || "1:66018666918:android:20460df1f06e3ffd3b4767",
      groups: "qa-team",
      release_notes: "New build from Fastlane 🚀\nBuilt at: #{Time.now.strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')}",
      apk_path: "../../build/app/outputs/flutter-apk/app-release.apk",
      firebase_cli_token: ENV["FIREBASE_CLI_TOKEN"]    # ← From `firebase login:ci`
    )

    UI.success("✅ Build distributed to Firebase successfully!")
  end

  # ─────────────────────────────────────────────
  # 🏪 Lane: Deploy to Google Play (Internal Testing)
  # ─────────────────────────────────────────────
  desc "Build App Bundle and deploy to Google Play Internal Testing"
  lane :deploy_internal do
    # Build App Bundle (required for Play Store)
    sh("cd ../.. && flutter build appbundle --release")

    upload_to_play_store(
      track: "internal",
      aab: "../../build/app/outputs/bundle/release/app-release.aab",
      skip_upload_metadata: true,
      skip_upload_images: true,
      skip_upload_screenshots: true,
      release_status: "draft"
    )

    UI.success("✅ App Bundle deployed to Play Store Internal Testing!")
  end

  # ─────────────────────────────────────────────
  # 🧪 Lane: Run Tests
  # ─────────────────────────────────────────────
  desc "Run Flutter tests"
  lane :test do
    sh("cd ../.. && flutter test")
    UI.success("✅ All tests passed!")
  end

end
